1-) Download Source Code and Extract it
2-) Start fwbuilder-bsgs.py with X-Forwarding
3-) Open Config Settings from Menu
4-) Unlock the settings
5-) Set Path Configs and Gitlab Configs ( Default Repo Path is /etc/fw/firewall/, you have to change it if u use any other from config.ini)
6-) Save Configs
7-) Turn Back to Main Window
8-) Start using it by starting Firewall Builder
9-) Change rules and Compile&Install it